{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/extras/Feature_Headline1.png?t=1737635732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into a strategic, tactical semi-auto battler with player agency through positioning and powerful activated ultimate abilities. Each hero comes with their own unique ability. Use it at the right time to turn the tide of battle, waste it, and risk a soul-crushing defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/extras/gold_framed_combat_3.gif?t=1737635732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/extras/Feature_Headline3.png?t=1737635732\" />Seer's Gambit is all about discovering the best group composition. Every character in the game can shine when combined with the right co-heroes. Unlock powerful combos by picking the perfect adventurers for your party and demolish your enemies with the power of teamwork.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/extras/framedsynergiessidebyside.gif?t=1737635732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/extras/Feature_Headline2.png?t=1737635732\" />Explore and upgrade the captivating, yet dangerous world of Emalon to unlock new heroes or powerful group buffs for meta progression. Earn resources during your adventures and predict the right upgrades to invest in for your heroes to stand a chance against the lurking evil. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you explore, progress and shape your future, the world will change around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/extras/framed_exploration_gif_with_steam_background.gif?t=1737635732\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mawelous","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/5330f51336d7fa506c74b0db07cd30bdff6b17c6.jpg"},{"name":"Incredible","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/0bc250fb12d6d96dbfd02c30ee39b4cd36bae2a3.jpg"},{"name":"A Royal Decree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/b460343c2f318bf7c2fb1385a9380a4aaf187592.jpg"},{"name":"You Candle Do it!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/d0fc30c4cadcc38c778d044341d5cfa447959757.jpg"},{"name":"Smelled the Roses","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/ef8d2469f54e8c93138f7641c798e5cf2fb378b1.jpg"},{"name":"There and Brack","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/7ea5a1fd732ac2273e219ae3a4081b142e8813cd.jpg"},{"name":"Going elsewhere fast!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/5bd73fa4afce1cb18d47c3c86ff94f327233d991.jpg"},{"name":"Yay!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/c252053fe7535b9bc1357a362107c148ccdeed8b.jpg"},{"name":"Almost!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/139b95f3b4fe2a624dd02ddd40758f341a6dc6a0.jpg"},{"name":"You\u2019ve Got This!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2219450/80b2eb90a1ed6ab98f92a6771fa66cdf2e414b47.jpg"}],"total":39},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737635732","background_raw":"